{
  "text": "This finding echoes earlier research highlighting that time constraints, the disparity between the available time and the time needed to address a task (Benson & Beach, 1996; Rastegary & Landy, 1993), can impact students' decision-making and task operation behavior (Gonzalez, 2004).",
